Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.24,0:22:52.43,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}醒來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.62,0:22:55.95,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}我還未被人發現的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.16,0:22:58.95,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}因為那一定不是錯覺啊
